  "StockRole": "Fire Support",
  "YangsThoughts": "Ceres Metals put this together as a joint project between the Confederation and the Magistracy, and honestly it shows. Reinforced Structure under all that Ferro-Fibrous plating means this thing shrugs off punishment that would wreck most other heavies. It is slow, but it does not need to be fast when everything shooting back at it is having such a hard time actually hurting it. Good machine to have on your side in a grinding fight.",
